quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  20,1,Tâ-Hâ
  20,2,ASikuthumelelanga i’Kur’ân (Muhammad) ukukuvisa ubuhlungu (emphefumlweni wakho)
  20,3,Koko (Siyithumelele) ukuba ibe yinkumbuzo kwabo baMoyikayo (uAllâh)
  20,4,IsiTyhilelo esivela kuYe (uAllâh) Owadala umhlaba namazulu aphakamileyo
  20,5,USolubabalo (uAllâh) Waphakamela ngentla kweTrone yaKhe
  20,6,"KokwaKhe konke okusemazulwini nako konke okusemhlabeni, nako konke okuphantsi komhlaba"
  20,7,"Kananjalo ukuba wena (Muhammad) uthetha ngokukhwaza (xa uthandazayo), inene Yena Wazi imfihlelo noko kufihlakele ngakumbi"
  20,8,"UAllâh, akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe ngawaKhe awona magama alungileyo"
  20,9,Ingaba ibali likaMûsâ lifikile na kuwe
  20,10,"Ukubona kwakhe umlilo, wathi kusapho lwakhe: “Lindani (apha)! Inene mna ndibone umlilo; mhlawumbi ndinganizela nesikhuni esivuthayo esiphuma kuwo, kungenjalo ndifumane isiKhokelo esithile emlilweni apho.”"
  20,11,"Wathi ke akufika kuwo, Wabizwa ngegama: “Hini na Mûsâ"
  20,12,"Inene Mna ndiyiNkosi yakho! Ngoko ke khulula iimbadada zakho, usentilini engcwele, iTuwâ"
  20,13,"Kananjalo Ndikunyule wena, phulaphula ke ngoko oko kuza kutyhilwa (kuwe)"
  20,14,"Inene! Mna ndinguAllâh. Akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaM, Khonza Mna ke, wenze iSalâh ukwenzela inkumbulo yaM"
  20,15,Inene iYure iyeza yaye Ndiphantse Ndiyifihle kwisiqu saM khon’ukuze umntu ngamnye avuzwe ngoko akusebenzelayo
  20,16,"Ngoko ke lowo ungakholwayo kuyo koko elandela iinkanuko zakhe makangakuphambukisi wena kuyo, kuba hleze utshabalale"
  20,17,Yintoni na leyo isesandleni sakho sokunene wena Mûsâ?”
  20,18,"Wathi yena (uMûsâ), “Yintonga yam, endisimelela ngayo, nendivuthululela izimvu zam amahlahla ngayo, ndenza neminye imisebenzi ngayo.”"
  20,19,"UAllâh Wathi: “Yijule phantsi ke Mûsâ!”"
  20,20,"Wayijula phantsi, yaza ngoko nangoko yaba yinyoka, irhubuluza ngokukhawuleza"
  20,21,"(UAllâh) Wathi, “Yibambe ungoyiki; Siya kuyibuyisela kwimo yayo yangaphambili"
  20,22,"Beka isandla sakho sokunene kwicala lakho lokhohlo: siya kubuya simhlophe, singenasifo (oko kuya) kuba ngomnye umqondiso"
  20,23,Khon’ukuze Sikubonise eminye yemqondiso emikhulu yeThu
  20,24,Hamba uye kuFir’awn (uFaro). Inene yena sele egabadele.”